const bodyHtml = "<main>\n      <div class=\"site-shell\">\n        <section class=\"hero\">\n          <span class=\"badge\">Month archive</span>\n          <h1>April 2026 guides</h1>\n          <p class=\"lede\">April focused on route quality, capital discipline and the first major systems patch of the spring cycle: safer NPC legs, seasonal recipe windows, the 0.24.3 systems refresh, a better Magic Find decision model and a practical mining loop that rewards execution more than glamour.</p>\n          <div class=\"button-row\">\n            <a class=\"button\" href=\"/guides\">Back to all guides</a>\n            <a class=\"button secondary\" href=\"/guides/march-2026\">Previous month: March 2026</a>\n            <a class=\"button secondary\" href=\"/guides/may-2026\">Next month: May 2026</a>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n          <div class=\"section-header\">\n            <span class=\"badge success\">Released in April</span>\n            <h2>Route optimization, patch analysis and ROI pages</h2>\n            <p>This stretch is about reading the market better and understanding the systems refresh that 0.24.3 brought: safer flips, better timing, a clearer idea of when a stat or route actually pays back, and the broader QoL changes that affect daily play.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"archive-grid\">\n            <article class=\"article-card\">\n              <span class=\"article-meta\">2026-04-06 • Bazaar Flipping</span>\n              <h3><a href=\"/guides/npc-to-bazaar-flips\">NPC to Bazaar Flips in Hypixel SkyBlock</a></h3>\n              <p>Daily caps, reverse-NPC routes and the items that stay boring enough to remain profitable.</p>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"article-card\">\n              <span class=\"article-meta\">2026-04-13 • Craft Flipping</span>\n              <h3><a href=\"/guides/seasonal-craft-flips-2026\">Seasonal Craft Flips in Hypixel SkyBlock</a></h3>\n              <p>How event pressure, mayor windows and temporary demand spikes change what counts as a good craft flip.</p>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"article-card\">\n              <span class=\"article-meta\">2026-04-18 • Patch Notes</span>\n              <h3><a href=\"/guides/hypixel-skyblock-0-24-3-update\">Hypixel SkyBlock 0.24.3 Update Guide</a></h3>\n              <p>Abiphone contacts, Littlefoot's Den, Jerry Island fishing refresh, greenhouse QoL and the market moves worth tracking from this broad systems patch.</p>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"article-card\">\n              <span class=\"article-meta\">2026-04-20 • Slayers</span>\n              <h3><a href=\"/guides/magic-find-slayer-roi\">Magic Find ROI for Slayer Grinding</a></h3>\n              <p>The slayer-by-slayer return on beacon upgrades, pet swaps and why ROI swings violently by boss type.</p>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"article-card\">\n              <span class=\"article-meta\">2026-04-27 • Mining</span>\n              <h3><a href=\"/guides/sludge-mining-guide\">Sludge Mining Guide for Hypixel SkyBlock</a></h3>\n              <p>Hardstone jungle routes, forging layers and the line between a solid sludge loop and a fully optimized money printer.</p>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n      </div>\n    </main>";
